<s> I strongly favor this alternative.  </s>
<s> The chain should stop when it returns to an already-known document, but other than that, I think it should be up to the application.  </s>
<s> I can see some applications only going a certain distance down the chain; others that silently follow the chain in the background, updating the display as they go; and others that just don't follow it at all.  </s>
<s> This is an excellent space for browsers to distinguish themselves in, and I think any one prescribed handling will break at least one possible application.  </s>
